text: Waterfront Park is a park along San Francisco's Embarcadero, near Pier 39, in the U.S. state of California. The park, established in 1976, is owned by the Port Authority. The park is home to the Skygate sculpture. ==See also== * List of parks in San Francisco ==References== ==External links== * Category:1976 establishments in California Category:Parks in San Francisco Category:North Beach, San Francisco Category:Fisherman's Wharf, San Francisco
